{
  "id": "6a05ad72ae51e04785e5e556",
  "title": "インドのパン",
  "created": 1778756979,
  "updated": 1778767114,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a05ad72ae51e04785e5e556",
      "text": "インドのパン",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe1",
      "text": "インドの[パン]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778760860
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe2",
      "text": "\t=[ロティ]？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe3",
      "text": "\t\tサンスクリット語でパンの意",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe4",
      "text": "\t\tよくわからない。チャパティはロティの一種といわれる。例えばパラタはそうではないの？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe5",
      "text": "\t種類が多すぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757641
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b0040000000000631006",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757637,
      "updated": 1778757637
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fe6",
      "text": " [パロタ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756985
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fec",
      "text": " [パラタ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757319
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630fef",
      "text": " [チャパティ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757362
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff0",
      "text": " [ドーサ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757363
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff1",
      "text": " [ワダ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757592
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff2",
      "text": " [イドゥリ]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757594
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05bca4000000000019e6c5",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778760868,
      "updated": 1778760868
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b00b0000000000631008",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757643,
      "updated": 1778757643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff3",
      "text": "\t[ティファン]/ティフィン",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757646
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff4",
      "text": "\t\t軽食の意",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff5",
      "text": "\t\tドーサ、ワダ、イドゥリなどがついてくるタイプのミールスがTiffinという認識である",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778757662
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05bc7e000000000019e6c2",
      "text": " \t\tミールスについてくることもあるそれらがTiffinということかも？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778760830,
      "updated": 1778760844
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05bc93000000000019e6c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778760852,
      "updated": 1778760852
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05bc93000000000019e6c4",
      "text": "[インド料理]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778760852,
      "updated": 1778760853
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05ad720000000000630ff6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778756979,
      "updated": 1778756979
    }
  ]
}